2025-08-27  Hayaki Saito <saitoha@me.com>

	* converters/img2sixel.1, converters/img2sixel.c,
	include/sixel.h.in, python/libsixel/__init__.py, src/encoder.c,
	src/quant.c: Add libsixel-specific error diffusion (dithering) to
	improve sixel compression by steering error propagation so out-of-palette intermediate colors
	render as horizontal bands rather than grainy noise, we increase RLE
	more effective.

